    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="/assets/css/APlayer.min.css"><script src="/assets/js/APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h2 id="PTE"><a href="#PTE" class="headerlink" title="PTE"></a>PTE</h2><blockquote><p>Pearson Test of English Academic: 培生英语语言测试</p></blockquote><blockquote><p>考试 71 道小题， 180分钟。<br><br/></p></blockquote><hr><h2 id="模考卷"><a href="#模考卷" class="headerlink" title="模考卷"></a>模考卷</h2><blockquote><p>官方模考卷分为A,B,C,三套, C卷很准， 实际考试会比C卷高 5-15 分</p></blockquote><blockquote><p>澳元价格随美元汇率浮动</p></blockquote><table><thead><tr><th>单卷</th><th>难度</th><th>实际考试相似度</th><th>美元</th><th>≈澳元</th><th>≈人民币</th><th>🥈Sliver</th><th>🥇Gold</th><th>💎Platinum</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>A</td><td>⭐️⭐️⭐️</td><td>⭐️</td><td>USD: 35.99</td><td>$57.07</td><td>¥254.88</td><td>✗</td><td>省¥42.46</td><td>省¥66.05</td></tr><tr><td>B</td><td>⭐️⭐️</td><td>⭐️⭐️</td><td>USD: 35.99</td><td>$57.07</td><td>¥254.88</td><td>✗</td><td>省¥42.46</td><td>省¥66.05</td></tr><tr><td>C</td><td>⭐️</td><td>⭐️⭐️⭐️</td><td>USD: 35.99</td><td>$57.07</td><td>¥254.88</td><td>省¥28.33</td><td>✗</td><td>省¥66.05</td></tr></tbody></table><table><thead><tr><th>套餐</th><th>内容</th><th>美元</th><th>≈澳元</th><th>≈人民币</th><th>共省</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>💎Platinum</td><td>Sample+A+B+C</td><td>USD: 79.99</td><td>$123.93</td><td>¥566.49</td><td>¥198.15</td></tr><tr><td>🥇Gold</td><td>Sample+A+B</td><td>USD: 59.99</td><td>$86.08</td><td>¥424.85</td><td>¥84.91</td></tr><tr><td>🥈Sliver</td><td>Sample+C</td><td>USD: 39.99</td><td>$57.38</td><td>¥283.21</td><td>¥28.33</td></tr></tbody></table><blockquote><p>模考切记使用苹果Airpod或其他蓝牙耳机， 我两次模考打水飘就因为用了蓝牙耳机， 模糊， 不识别。</p></blockquote><blockquote><p>如果用了蓝牙耳机发音没有分， 可以截图， 通过官网申诉获得模考重制, 😈亲测重制了A,B,C三套卷。</p></blockquote><br/><hr><h2 id="PTE-对应-IELTS-分数"><a href="#PTE-对应-IELTS-分数" class="headerlink" title="PTE 对应 IELTS 分数"></a>PTE 对应 IELTS 分数</h2><br/><p><img src="/assets/images/pteScoreConversion.jpg" alt="成绩对标"></p><br/><table><thead><tr><th>SoE</th><th></th><th></th><th></th><th></th><th></th><th>👇🏻</th><th>⇉</th><th>⭐</th><th></th><th></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>PTE</td><td><del>30</del></td><td><del>36</del></td><td><del>42</del></td><td><del>50</del></td><td><del>58</del></td><td><green>65</green></td><td>73</td><td>79</td><td>83</td><td>86</td></tr><tr><td>IELTS</td><td><del>4.5</del></td><td><del>5.0</del></td><td><del>5.5</del></td><td><del>6.0</del></td><td><del>6.5</del></td><td><green>7.0</green></td><td>7.5</td><td>8.0</td><td>8.5</td><td>9.0</td></tr></tbody></table><br><hr><h2 id="PTE保-6-5-分析"><a href="#PTE保-6-5-分析" class="headerlink" title="PTE保 6.5 分析"></a>PTE保 6.5 分析</h2><table><thead><tr><th>目标分数</th><th>64分</th><th>正确率</th><th>重点复习</th><th>每日</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>朗读原文</td><td>RA</td><td><y>4</y> / <strong>6</strong></td><td>⭐️⭐️⭐️</td><td><strong>12</strong></td></tr><tr><td>重复句子</td><td>RS</td><td><y>3</y> / <strong>9</strong></td><td>⭐️⭐️⭐️</td><td><strong>40</strong></td></tr><tr><td>描述图片</td><td>DI</td><td><y>3</y> / <strong>6</strong></td><td>⭐️⭐️⭐️</td><td><strong>8</strong></td></tr><tr><td>复述演讲</td><td>RL</td><td><y>3</y> / <strong>4</strong></td><td>⭐️⭐️⭐️</td><td><strong>8</strong></td></tr><tr><td>短句问答</td><td>ASQ</td><td><y>9</y> / <strong>9</strong></td><td>⭐️</td><td><strong>20</strong></td></tr><tr><td>短文简写</td><td>SWT</td><td><y>2</y> / <strong>2</strong></td><td>⭐️⭐️⭐️</td><td><strong>8</strong></td></tr><tr><td>短文写作</td><td>WE</td><td><y>1</y> / <strong>1</strong></td><td>⭐️⭐️</td><td><strong>8</strong></td></tr><tr><td>阅读单选</td><td>MCS</td><td><strong>2</strong> / <strong>2</strong></td><td>⭐️</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>阅读多选</td><td>MCM</td><td><strong>2</strong> / <strong>2</strong></td><td>⭐️</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>段落排序</td><td>RP</td><td><strong>2</strong> / <strong>2</strong></td><td>⭐️</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>拖词填空</td><td>FIB</td><td><strong>3</strong> / <strong>3</strong></td><td>⭐️⭐️</td><td><strong>20</strong></td></tr><tr><td>选词填空</td><td>FIB</td><td><strong>5</strong> / <strong>5</strong></td><td>⭐️⭐️</td><td><strong>20</strong></td></tr><tr><td>录音总结</td><td>SST</td><td><strong>2</strong> / <strong>2</strong></td><td>⭐️⭐️</td><td><strong>8</strong></td></tr><tr><td>听力多选</td><td>MCM</td><td><strong>2</strong> / <strong>2</strong></td><td>⭐️</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>听词填空</td><td>FIB</td><td><strong>2</strong> / <strong>2</strong></td><td>⭐️⭐️</td><td><strong>8</strong></td></tr><tr><td>摘要单选</td><td>HCS</td><td><strong>2</strong> / <strong>2</strong></td><td>⭐️</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>听力单选</td><td>MCS</td><td><strong>2</strong> / <strong>2</strong></td><td>⭐️</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>补全对话</td><td>SMW</td><td><strong>2</strong> / <strong>2</strong></td><td>⭐️</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>识别错词</td><td>HIW</td><td><strong>2</strong> / <strong>2</strong></td><td>⭐️</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>听写句子</td><td>WFD</td><td><strong>2</strong> / <strong>2</strong></td><td>⭐️⭐️⭐️</td><td><strong>40</strong></td></tr></tbody></table><br><hr><h2 id="考试顺序-amp-分析"><a href="#考试顺序-amp-分析" class="headerlink" title="考试顺序&amp;分析"></a>考试顺序&amp;分析</h2><table>    <thead>        <tr>            <th>分节</th>            <th>项目</th>            <th>耗时</th>            <th>题型</th>            <th>简称</th>            <th colspan=2>权重</th>            <th>题量</th>            <th>单分</th>            <th>评分方式</th>            <th colspan=2>考察能力</th>        </tr>    </thead>    <tbody>    <!-- 写作 -->    <tr>        <tr>            <!-- 口语 -->            <td rowspan=15>1                <tr>                    <td rowspan=10><green>口语</green>                        <tr>                            <tr>                                <td rowspan=12>77-93/M</td>                            <tr>                            <tr>                                <td colspan=6>自我介绍</td>                            </tr>                            <tr>                                <td><green>朗读原文</green></td>        